Edward Mothibi has won this year's Comrades Marathon. DURBAN - Edward Mothibi has won this year's Comrades Marathon. This is Mothibi's first Comrades Marathon win after finishing fourth last year. Last year's winner Bongumusa Mthembu finished second. The 94th edition of the world’s most gruelling ultramarathon spans 86km from Durban to Pietermaritzburg. 